Summary:. I was looking for a flash drive for Windows ready boost. I found the Sandisk cruzer Micro to be the cheapest(i found it for 20.00!), and to work great with ready boost! It comes preloaded with tons of security, photo, and game apps.Plus it has 2 GB of memory! But, it does have pretty slow file transfer with pictures and media. So, if you want a all-in-one flash drive for a cheap price, The Sandisk Cruzer Micro is for you!!!. 

