Cons:. scraches easily, slow file transfer. 
Summary:. Yes it is a bit on the slow side, but i really like the retractable design (much better than a cap that will get lost). I threw it away by mistake while cleaning out my car, and when i found it in the dumpster in 2" of dirty water I was worried that it would not work anymore. I let it dry and it is fine.. 

