Summary:. Ultimately it's a flash-based memory thingy and it does this well-enough. I can't say I'm dissatisfied with it's write speed, but I'm not timing it against other units eithers.. I will say that I DO NOT like the way it intrusively installs software without my permission. I detest any and all hardware that does this and this is no exception.. Was on sale at Best Buy for $39.99. Hard to beat that price.. 

